title: War of the Roses: He Had a Holiday Inn Coffee Cup
description: Laura's husband was supposed to be having a boy's night but he came home with a Holiday Inn coffee cup.  As in, he had stayed at a Holiday Inn overnight and grabbed some coffee on the way out.  That doesn't seem like someone you would get from a boy's night, so where did the cup come from?
